      "content": "hey so my doctor prescribed me some diazepam to help with my insomnia cuz i havent been sleeping well lately. i was wondering if it's okay to have like a small glass of red wine with my dose at night? i feel like it might actually help me relax even faster so i can pass out. is that safe for light use?",
