      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that it's not ideal but i'm not talking about getting drunk lol. just like, one glass of wine to take the edge off. won't the alcohol just work with the medicine to help me sleep better? it seems like they both do the same thing so shouldn't they just kind of help each other out?",
